examples.en: She did astonishingly well in her exams.
Even as a child he was astonishingly inventive.
Its been, astonishingly, five years since my last visit.
She has an astonishingly vivid memory.
Astonishingly, the dog swam across the lake.
The cello sonata was astonishingly beautiful.
The black vote is astonishingly loyal to the Democratic Party.
